OL,3,CUlez fine evaders face bankruptcy
OL,4,Cthreat
OL,6,FDrivers who persistently refuse to pay
OL,7,Fultra-low emission zone (Ulez) fines
OL,8,Fcould be made bankrupt, Transport for
OL,9,FLondon (TfL) has said.
OL,11,FThe transport authority made the claim
OL,12,Fas it vowed to enhance its crackdown
OL,13,Fon a "specific group of drivers" with
OL,14,Flong-standing Ulez debts.
OL,16,FSome 94% of Ulez debt is owed by
OL,17,Fpeople with at least four outstanding
OL,18,Fpenalty charge notices (PCNs).
