OL,6,FTfL said it "continues to ramp up its
OL,7,Fefforts to deliver stronger
OL,8,Fenforcement", which in "extreme cases"
OL,9,Fcould lead to an individual facing
OL,10,F"bankruptcy proceedings" if they
OL,11,Frefuse to settle their debts.
OL,13,FOther action could include ensuring
OL,14,Fdebts are paid before a property is
OL,15,Fsold, and recovering money from a
OL,16,Fperson's earnings through their
OL,17,Femployer.
