OL,6,FTfL is also trialling changes to the
OL,7,Fstyle and format of its PCNs, aimed at
OL,8,Fexplaining the process better in an
OL,9,Fattempt to encourage more recipients
OL,10,Fto pay up.
OL,12,FThe authority said it was deploying an
OL,13,F"intelligence-led approach" which
OL,14,Fincluded tracking evaders down to
OL,15,Fdifferent addresses and more effective
OL,16,Fdata sharing with national bodies such
OL,17,Fas the Department for Transport and
OL,18,Fthe Driver and Vehicle Licensing
OL,19,FAuthority.
