OL,6,FThis led to around #16.5 million of
OL,7,Fdebt related to road-user charges and
OL,8,Fpenalties being recovered between
OL,9,FJanuary and June, according to TfL.
OL,11,FMore than 530 vehicles were seized by
OL,12,Fenforcement agents over that period.
OL,14,FAlex Williams, TfL's chief customer
OL,15,Fand strategy officer, said: "With 97%
OL,16,Fof vehicles seen driving in London now
OL,17,FUlez compliant, only a very small
OL,18,Fminority of vehicles now don't meet
OL,19,Fthe standards.
