OL,3,CUlez fine evaders face bankruptcy
OL,4,Cthreat
OL,6,F"Most drivers who have vehicles that
OL,7,Fare liable for the charge are
OL,8,Fresponsible and pay it.
OL,10,F"It is only a small group of
OL,11,Fpersistent evaders who fail to do so.
OL,13,F"We want to make it clear that if you
OL,14,Freceive a penalty charge for driving
OL,15,Fin the zone, you should not ignore it.
OL,17,F"Your penalty will progress to
OL,18,Fenforcement agents to recover what you
OL,19,Fowe, and there is a risk that your
OL,20,Fvehicle and other items of property
OL,21,Fwill be removed."
