OL,6,FMayor of London Sir Sadiq Khan
OL,7,Fextended the Ulez from everywhere
OL,8,Fwithin the North and South Circular
OL,9,Froads to cover all London boroughs on
OL,10,FAugust 29 2023, creating the world's
OL,11,Fbiggest pollution charging zone.
OL,13,FFor petrol cars to meet the Ulez
OL,14,Frequirement, they must generally have
OL,15,Fbeen first registered after 2005.
OL,17,FMost diesel cars must have been
OL,18,Fregistered after September 2015 to be
OL,19,Fexempt.
