OL,6,FMost vehicles that do not meet minimum
OL,7,Femissions standards and do not benefit
OL,8,Ffrom exemptions are required to pay a
OL,9,F#12.50 daily fee for entering the Ulez.
OL,11,FNon-payment can lead to a PCN, which
OL,12,Fcan escalate up to #280 if ignored.
OL,14,FAt the end of the last financial year,
OL,15,Fthe total value of unpaid Ulez PCNs
OL,16,Fwas #789.1 million.
OL,18,FThis included money expected to be
OL,19,Fpaid as well as amounts owed by
OL,20,Fpersistent evaders.
